name: Tracer
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: TRACER is a sustainable M2E project on Web3. Each TRACER NFT shoe is composed of 4 NFT shoe parts, each aesthetic and unique. TRACER's sustainable tokenomics is backed up by burning NFTs & tokens by web2 & web3 revenue, plus deflationary social-games and composable 3D NFTs.
